==Hindi==
===Etymology===
From the [[Prakrit]] लम्बओ and Sanskrit लम्ब+कः

===Adjective===
'''लम्बा''' (lambā)
# [[tall]] (of people)
# [[long]] (of objects, duration, etc)
# expanded, great, large
# spacious, capacious

===Alternative spelling=== 
*[[लंबा]]

